```plantuml
@startuml sfujiwara_terraform-google-ai-platform-notification

actor User
participant "AI Platform" as AI
participant "Logging Sink" as Sink
participant "ai_platform_log\nPub/Sub Topic" as LogTopic
participant "Cloud Function" as Function
participant "Notification\nPub/Sub Topic" as NotifyTopic
participant "Subscriber" as Subscriber

User -> AI: Submit Training Job
AI -> Sink: Generate Logs (state changes)
Sink -> LogTopic: Publish Log Messages
LogTopic -> Function: Trigger with Log Message

alt Job State Change Detected
    Function -> Function: Parse Log\n(extract job details)
    Function -> NotifyTopic: Publish Notification
    NotifyTopic -> Subscriber: Deliver Notification
else No State Change
    Function -> Function: Ignore Log Message
end

@enduml
```